title: Celebrating creativity at Design Manchester (Manchester Metropolitan University)
text: ( Source : Manchester Metropolitan University ) School of Art-backed festival returns for third year THE most exciting design festival in the calendar starts this week, and Manchester School of Art are proud to once again be heavily involved.
